content:
Sure! Here are some ancient Greek-based words that could work as names for a baby milestone app:

1. Arche (meaning "beginning")
2. Proodos (meaning "progress")
3. Anatasis (meaning "growth")
4. Prokairesis (meaning "advancement")
5. Protos Vima (meaning "first steps")
6. Physis (meaning "nature")
7. Metamorphosis (meaning "transformation")
8. Episteme (meaning "knowledge")
9. Neos Kosmos (meaning "new world")
10. Agon (meaning "contest" or "struggle")
